title: Amy Thinks Her Crossing Guard Is Shady + The Shell-On Challenge
itunes:title: Amy Thinks Her Crossing Guard Is Shady + The Shell-On Challenge
description:
Amy thinks her crossing guard might be up to no good and starts an investigation. Show members have to eat an entire food item in the "shell-on challenge". Our girl group share their thoughts on the correct anniversary date for couples.
